<TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">I don't think the majority of the problems we're having are because of the processors or video cards.  Problem seems to be with the sound.  Almost everyone experiences the lousy sound now, and many people are crashing.<P>In my case, it was the sound that was causing the lockups and the blue screens of death.  I finally disabled directsound hardware acceleration and opened up DXDIAG and cranked down the sound setting to normal.  That fixed everything.</FONT>
</TD></TR>

